      {
        "title": "Choosing a Simple Melody",
        "content": "Select a melody you enjoy. Popular choices include:\n- 'Twinkle, Twinkle, Little Star'\n- 'Mary Had a Little Lamb'\n- 'Ode to Joy'"
      },
      {
        "title": "Focusing on Rhythm",
        "content": "Pay attention to the timing:\n- Count beats aloud.\n- Use a metronome for practice.\n- Start slow, then increase speed."
      },
      {
        "title": "Hand Position and Technique",
        "content": "Maintain proper hand posture:\n- Keep fingers curved.\n- Use fingertips to press keys.\n- Relax your shoulders and wrists."
      }
    ]
  }
}
